Current Build Commands
======================

Note: I have copied AVR128DB48def.inc and AVR128DB64.inc to the include/ and modified

#pragma AVRPART CORE CORE_VERSION V4

to

#pragma AVRPART CORE CORE_VERSION V2E

to avoid the warnings, as the avrasm2 versions for macOS do not know about the core
versin v4


avrasm2 -v2 -fI -o main-v2-1.hex  -m main-v2-1.map  -l main-v2-1.lss  -S main-v2-1.tmp  -W+ie -I ~/AVR-Projects/include/  -iAVR128DB64def.inc    main-v2-1.asm





