2022-01-22
===========

pymcuprog allows to read back the memory also from dead MCUs

pymcuprog read -d avr128db48 -m internal_sram -f sram

You can also read just a section with -o (offset) and -b (bytes) however after
the read the MCU will be reset and reexecute the loaded programm that will
most likely initialise the internal SRAM again

hexdump -C sram_internal_sram.bin | more
